@startuml dylanvanh_MunchOut

actor Customer
actor Restaurant
participant "Flutter Frontend" as Frontend
participant "AuthBloc" as AuthBloc
participant "UserRepository" as UserRepo
participant "CustomerRepository" as CustomerRepo
participant "RestaurantRepository" as RestaurantRepo
participant "Flask API" as API
database "Database" as DB

== Authentication ==
Customer -> Frontend: Login/Signup
Frontend -> AuthBloc: Authenticate
AuthBloc -> UserRepo: Validate credentials
UserRepo -> API: POST /auth
API -> DB: Verify user
DB --> API: User data
API --> UserRepo: Authentication response
UserRepo --> AuthBloc: Auth result
AuthBloc --> Frontend: Update auth state

== Customer Flow ==
Customer -> Frontend: Browse events
Frontend -> CustomerRepo: Get events
CustomerRepo -> API: GET /events
API -> DB: Fetch events
DB --> API: Event data
API --> CustomerRepo: Event list
CustomerRepo --> Frontend: Display events

Customer -> Frontend: Book event
Frontend -> CustomerRepo: Create booking
CustomerRepo -> API: POST /bookings
API -> DB: Save booking
DB --> API: Booking confirmation
API --> CustomerRepo: Booking result
CustomerRepo --> Frontend: Confirm booking

== Restaurant Flow ==
Restaurant -> Frontend: Create event
Frontend -> RestaurantRepo: Submit event
RestaurantRepo -> API: POST /events
API -> DB: Save event
DB --> API: Event confirmation
API --> RestaurantRepo: Event creation result
RestaurantRepo --> Frontend: Confirm event creation

Restaurant -> Frontend: View bookings
Frontend -> RestaurantRepo: Get bookings
RestaurantRepo -> API: GET /restaurant/bookings
API -> DB: Fetch bookings
DB --> API: Booking data
API --> RestaurantRepo: Booking list
RestaurantRepo --> Frontend: Display bookings

@enduml